Global Patient Support Equipments Market Insights
Patient Support Equipments Market size was valued at USD 13.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 21.5 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Patient Support Equipments Market Overview
The global Patient Support Equipment Market was valued at USD 11.2 billion in 2023 and is projected to reach USD 17.9 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.4% during the forecast period. This growth is fueled by the increasing elderly population, rising chronic disease prevalence, and advancements in healthcare infrastructure. The demand for patient support equipment such as patient lifts, beds, wheelchairs, and monitoring devices is on the rise globally. These equipment provide crucial support for patients in both hospital and home care settings, ensuring safety, comfort, and improved outcomes.

